The title of the paper mentions "formal techniques" and "design and analysis," which are indicative of software engineering (cs.SE) and programming languages (cs.PL). The workshop focuses on the Overture tool, which is used for formal modelling and analysis of systems, suggesting a connection to logic (cs.LO) and modelling and simulation (cs.MS). Finally, the use of formal techniques in the design and analysis of systems is also relevant to artificial intelligence (cs.AI).
